{"tid":1997233,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[快Ｄcheck] 有部分市民可能冇左超區選民資格！","createTime":"2020-05-01T13:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T07:33:55.000Z","uid":100581,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"225f8ead2d5ce03d0560a67547d5724eceeef9fe","tid":1997233,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5svmnAsgNJ4&amp;t=8m08s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5svmnAsgNJ4%26t%3D8m08s&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw19mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=f137326c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5svmnAsgNJ4&amp;t=8m08s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果2015 , 2016, 2017 選民登記個陣，有tick到超區個一格既話<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有部分選民有可能冇左黎緊超區選民資格！</span></strong><br />\n選民資料網上查閱系統：[url]<a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw19mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=7c2eae3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n如果冇左，聽晚23:59分前入返表就拎得返個資格！<br />\n唔該各路手足幫手推！"},{"pid":"5339e6379c6a908b03d6a45ae447bca0570e836c","tid":1997233,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4981689eab101a32d2f37080c59a06eac13968f7","tid":1997233,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4f6033fc8dcb2572fd58fb2387060889886023","tid":1997233,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.